item.description:
@Cryme_Time wrote:

If you don’t know were to add these search an existing command in client.java and paste this under it.

The first 28 items

if (command.startsWith("silabitems1") && playerRights >= 0) { addItem(7621, 1); addItem(7622, 1); addItem(7623, 1); addItem(7624, 1); addItem(7625, 1); addItem(7626, 1); addItem(7627, 1); addItem(7628, 1); addItem(7629, 1); addItem(7630, 1); addItem(7631, 1); addItem(7632, 1); addItem(7633, 1); addItem(7634, 1); addItem(7635, 1); addItem(7636, 1); addItem(7637, 1); addItem(7638, 1); addItem(7639, 1); addItem(7640, 1); addItem(7641, 1); addItem(7642, 1); addItem(7643, 1); addItem(7644, 1); addItem(7645, 1); addItem(7646, 1); addItem(7647, 1); addItem(7648, 1); sendMessage("You receive 28 of silabs items"); }
The next 28 items

if (command.startsWith("silabitems2") && playerRights >= 0) { addItem(7649, 1); addItem(7650, 1); addItem(7651, 1); addItem(7652, 1); addItem(7643, 1); addItem(7654, 1); addItem(7655, 1); addItem(7656, 1); addItem(7657, 1); addItem(7658, 1); addItem(7659, 1); addItem(7660, 1); addItem(7661, 1); addItem(7662, 1); addItem(7663, 1); addItem(7664, 1); addItem(7665, 1); addItem(7666, 1); addItem(7667, 1); addItem(7668, 1); addItem(7669, 1); addItem(7670, 1); addItem(7671, 1); addItem(7672, 1); addItem(7673, 1); addItem(7674, 1); addItem(7675, 1); addItem(7676, 1); sendMessage("You receive 28 of silabs items"); }
The last few items

if (command.startsWith("silabitems3") && playerRights >= 0) { addItem(7677, 1); addItem(7678, 1); addItem(7679, 1); addItem(7680, 1); addItem(7681, 1); addItem(7682, 1); addItem(7683, 1); addItem(7684, 1); }

This is up-To-Date with the newest items, the commands for them are ::silabitems1-3 (if you don’t know) and player rights is set at “0”, so use it well, post feedback please.

If this is the wrong section please tell me.
